subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Failing to qualify for the Chase for the Nextel Cup has not prevented defending Nascar champ Tony Stewart from stealing some late-season thunder from this year’s title contenders.
